<plot>This documentary depicts the creation of the novel by V. Alexander Stefan entitled "Doctor Faustef." The novel deals with the "Marie Louise Bromfield Immortality Experiment," which Faustef performed on his two graduate students and himself on February 11, 2001. The experiment was based on ephemerons, the particles of time, in interaction with "the gate of immortality" located in our brains. In that experiment their mortal existence code-5 has been transmuted into immortal code-7.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248073</url></doc>
